    <description>Detect outdated Terraform modules and providers with breaking change analysis, upgrade paths, and governance recommendations.

## Features
- Scans Terraform dependencies (modules and providers)
- Detects breaking changes in Azure Verified Modules (AVM)
- Lock file awareness (.terraform.lock.hcl)
- Safe auto-fix for non-breaking updates
- MCP server for AI assistant integration
    </description>
    <summary>Terraform dependency scanner with breaking change detection</summary>
    <tags>terraform infrastructure-as-code devops azure iac</tags>
